channel.title: Server won't Go Online?
channel.description: I have finnally finished coding my server, which took me about a month. I got No-ip, and it has an IP. I opened the port 43594. I logged in with the 0.0.0.0 IP and it worked. Then, I tried the Runelocus server status thingy, and it said offline? I also tried registsring on the serverstatus. Still nothing. Can you please help? I did do portforwarding put it didnt work? Any tuts? I have a NETGEAR WGR614 v9 Router PLEASE HELP
